<img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105016JLCKySmM3eDudnk1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105017z0V8EGD9frUlovqF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105017KZlwSFyPjLXpuaMh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105108ib5If7Exz3GYUkLh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105110ArLvP912f3oGhz7N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105111CTrqAZtKzgvb3jQp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105112gTKti7P6450AQz1I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105113JVhglTy8vjUG6ibI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105113izGpHcrRKqyDv1jh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105116iAg36BS049fWX7Nb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/calvin-klein-talks-seductive-advertising-and-minimalism-in-new-book-11032800/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Calvin Klein</a> 出了一本同名新书，由其本人撰写、编辑，图片选自其 30 年职业生涯中的 40000 多张广告大片及摄影作品，售价 150 美元、共 463 页。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105550U4PpsYLV7EcWbiIf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.794271\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105252MVRZJ175yBqTYsSH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/25/ugg-for-men-fall-winter-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">UGG 和 Phillip Lim 的最新设计师合作款男鞋系列</a>出炉，看宣传大片比上一波单品似乎要好看一点。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710261053300c9tHG1IB8Uix4PD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105334gBFkZx5n0IsqdhTz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105330VfAwTWt2kHSUzPO8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105330mvoKxUC1q4PRHfWr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>The North Face 2017 秋冬出了个 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/10/the-north-face-2017-fall-winter-international-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">International 系</a>列，以美国和韩国的国旗元素为主要的设计灵感，带来了羽绒服、背包、帽子、围巾、鞋子等花哨的单品。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105410mdNoXwsikJp0vrlY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666144\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017102610544014bXeVNxQ3n260mC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667153\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105411aXrBDztxwbM2Ah90.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Dolce &amp; Gabbana 和意大利电器品牌 Smeg 合作，推出了一个浮夸的西西里风情的限量版<a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/article/dolce-and-gabbana-designer-smeg-refrigerator\" rel=\"nofollow\">冰箱</a>系列。<br></p><p>这系列冰箱限量 100 个，据说冰箱上繁复的图案都是由 Domenico Dolce 和 Stefano Gabbana 亲自挑选画家手工绘制而成，售价 5 万美元一台。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710261055078is6cvFBQkGbYHCT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105507MgCm273RHboB9LcP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710261055080HPeYw5rpRZ3Gsdt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017102610551292QMLXdpKaRV1oxk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667480\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026105527OfCyI7am0bXKeghr.gif\" data-ratio=\"1.592920\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>题图来自：UGG</p>"}